&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on role. You will work directly in the codebase, agent system, and infrastructure while leading a small team of engineers. You will be responsible for making the system work in practice and tying it to business outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role reports directly to the CEO.&lt;/p&gt;
